Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:02.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.65,0:00:04.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:06.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scars that just refuse to fade\Nfrom memory
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:09.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes the burden’s too much\Nfor one to bear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:12.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t give up on me,\Nplease don’t turn me away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:15.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:18.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll hold your hand in mine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:25.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will I lose my hold on her someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:32.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will her smile fade  In a flood of tears\NOr can I keep the fears at bay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:37.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Echoing, distant voices wither into silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:42.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one thing that\Nwill never ever age…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:46.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my love for you is timeless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:48.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:50.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:52.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Smiles with hearts’ bitterness replaced
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never smile again”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:54.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never let love in”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:57.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t ever say such things to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:00.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A future we cannot see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:03.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All happenings\NFind meaning in the story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:07.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In time the clouds will clear away,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:11.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so just stay, please stay with me…\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:17.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are we to pass through you?\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:19.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That answer will find you someday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:30.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But still, if it’s true what\Nthat bald guy said,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:34.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and even if Rukia is in\Nthat white tower…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.31,0:01:38.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is which road\Nto take to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:39.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that’s right. I have a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:46.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn’t want to run into\Nany Captains along the way, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.99,0:01:50.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia… Are you talking\Nabout Rukia Kuchiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:50.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:53.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought…\NIt’s her, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:58.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then that “white tower” you referred to\Nis the Senzaikyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.21,0:02:05.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I…know the hidden way\Ninto that tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.95,0:02:15.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, I would have never thought\Nof using the sewer system.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:20.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this sewer system runs\Nunderground throughout the Seireitei,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:23.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so we can go anywhere\Nwithout running into obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:27.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t the others know\Nabout this entrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.52,0:02:30.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was under an ordinary-looking tile…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.03,0:02:33.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, everyone knows about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:36.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I doubt they’ll catch up\Nwith us down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:36.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:41.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones that fully comprehend\Nthis complex system
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:42.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,are members of Squad 4,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:45.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,those of us who specialize\Nin relief and aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:49.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see, this system is also used\Nas a pathway for relief and aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:53.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why only the relief and aid company\Nneeded to master this system.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:55.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not exactly…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:03:02.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s just that it’s Squad 4’s duty\Nto clean up the sewer system.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:04.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’re weak, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:06.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we wind up\Nwith a lot of menial chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:11.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gee, I kind of feel sorry\Nfor this Squad 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:14.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No… It’s really not all that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:18.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hanataro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:18.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:23.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing all this for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’re your enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And just because we want\Nto go to the White Tower…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.09,0:03:34.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guiding us\Nwithout question?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:40.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know a lot about you…\Nfrom listening to Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:42.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:48.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please… Save Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here is the situation report.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:57.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Ikkaku Madarame,\NThird Seat of Squad 11,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:04:01.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and Sir Yumichika Ayasegawa,\NFifth Seat, same squad…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:04.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The above high-ranking Seat officers,\Ndue to serious injuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,will withdraw from the front lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:10.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A detailed damage report\Nfor the individual squads
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,is still pending investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:16.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, regarding Squad 11…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:19.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is a report stating that\Nthey were nearly annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 11?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:24.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:27.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In just a few hours since\Nentering this realm,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:28.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,they’ve managed to wreak\Nthat much havoc?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:31.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah, how pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:34.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At this time, there are three\Nconfirmed Ryoka,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:36.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,of which two have taken\Na member of the Squad 4 hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:38.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We have intelligence indicating\Nthat these two, with the hostage,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,are headed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:42.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, since a while ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:44.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we have been unable to detect\Ntheir Spiritual Pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:46.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,therefore, their whereabouts\Nare unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:57.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, we need to collect\Nmore information.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:05:02.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly, it’s been a while since\Nour Fourth Seat reported in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:04.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think he’s been defeated too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:06.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you check in\Non the West 20 area?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Fourth Seat of Squad 7…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:13.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Jirobo –\Nthe Kamaitachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:14.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:19.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jidanbo’s brother, huh?\NHe’s defeated too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:21.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:26.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, they’re all pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.23,0:05:29.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This certainly has turned\Ninto a horrible mess, Abarai…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:28.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We need to act more carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:32.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That Squad 11 gets too temperamental.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:35.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You, stop spreading misinformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Abarai…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:37.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I did no such thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:38.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:52.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Before Rukia was captured and\Nplaced in the Senzaikyu Shishinro,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:55.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,she was held\Nin Squad 6’s barracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:06:00.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was assigned to cleaning duty\Nfor that area.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:05.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest,\NI was scared of her at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:07.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she is nobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:09.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:10.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:14.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia scolded me on my first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:20.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Miss Rukia, I’ll be starting\Ntoday’s cleaning chores now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:24.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’d rather you not call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… But…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:28.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just address me normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:34.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh?  Umm… Ah…\NThen… Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:36.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:38.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:42.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Her voice was much kinder\Nthan what I had expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:45.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was quite relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:49.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that day,\Nmy daily cleaning at the barracks
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.79,0:06:52.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,gradually has become something\Nto look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:58.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And little by little, Rukia started\Ntelling me all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:04.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Rukia? I don’t know much\Nabout the human world,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:05.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but what’s it like over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:07.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Like the things to eat or drink…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:09.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:12.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it’s nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:18.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They have a beverage called a\N“juice” that comes in a paper package.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of a drink is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:25.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is a difficult beverage…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:27.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:35.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is a trick to drinking it.\NEven I had difficulties with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:41.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? There’s a drink that\Neven you had difficulties with…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:45.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hanataro, you may not be able to drink\Nit even after hearing the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:45.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:50.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That guy,\Nhe taught me how to drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:56.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, was there anything unusual\Nin the human world?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:58.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that\Na Mod Konpaku
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:01.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,can be inserted into\Ninanimate objects as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You mean those illegal things?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:08.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There was this guy who placed one\Ninto a stuffed doll found on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:10.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stuffed doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:13.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the thing made with\Ncotton and such, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:16.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To put it into something like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:18.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There sure are some reckless folks\Nout there…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:23.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… There are some\Nreckless ones out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:29.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the tales Rukia told me\Nof the human world…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:35.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the majority of them were always\Nabout this one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:42.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shortly thereafter, an official\Nexecution order was sent to Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:44.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t make me repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:47.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For a first-degree offense,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:50.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia Kuchiki shall be held\Nin maximum security.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:52.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In 25 days, she shall be sent
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:55.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to the Central Execution Grounds\Nto be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:06.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia… The person you gave\Nyour Soul Reaper powers to…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:09.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the same person\Nyou often speak of?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:11.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Ichigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:17.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I only spent two months with him,\Nbut strangely,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:20.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I felt I could trust him from\Nthe bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:21.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And yet…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:23.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And yet…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:29.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Because of me, his destiny became twisted\Nand he was terribly hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:32.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing I can do\Nto atone for this…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:37.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She looked very sad\Nas she said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:46.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How’d you say?\NShe’s a strange Soul Reaper, that one…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:49.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she’s a strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.89,0:09:50.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:53.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why we’re here\Nto rescue her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ah? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:56.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:58.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:09:59.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:01.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:07.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I only spent two months with him…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:11.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but strangely, I felt I could trust him\Nfrom the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:44.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, because of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:47.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,his destiny became twisted\Nand he was terribly hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:51.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing I can do\Nto atone for this…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:57.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot! Isn’t that all my fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:09.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, I won’t let you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:10.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:24.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… It’s okay! You can come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:27.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This exit is the closest to the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:32.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It seems like a long time since\NI’ve breathed fresh air!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:35.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There, that’s the Senzaikyu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:41.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’re definitely closer to it,\Nbut look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:46.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it’s going to be\Na rough road ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:48.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The mist is clearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:55.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:07.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:12.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There’s someone by the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:29.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:33.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:37.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would have liked to forget it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:41.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but there’s still a mountain\Nof payback I owe you…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:43.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji Abarai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:04.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s a surprise,\Nyou remembered my name, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:11.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:19.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His Spirit Pressure is on a completely\Ndifferent level than those earlier guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-That, that person is…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji Abarai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:30.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Lieutenant of Squad 6!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:36.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m truly surprised…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:42.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you’d be dead after\NCaptain Kuchiki’s attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:49.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, hey! Wait a minute, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:52.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know how you managed\Nto survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:54.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but you’re something else, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:08.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But this is as far as you go.\NAs I’ve told you before,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:11.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will kill the one who stole\NRukia’s powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:17.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you’re alive,\NRukia can’t get her powers back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:20.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that after\Ntaking her back just to kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:23.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Try it if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:26.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If only you can defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:40.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s starting,\Nand the opponent is Abarai, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:43.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He’s already defeated\Nthe Third Seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:47.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Next, he had better defeat\Nat least a Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, he won’t be much fun\Nas my opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:54.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kenny, how is it that you don’t sense\Nother people’s Spirit Pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:57.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but you can tell they’re fighting\Nfrom far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:00.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s because I’m strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.89,0:15:03.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… That’s weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:07.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you found anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:10.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s been a while since these\NRyoka crossed over
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:14.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and while our casualties keep rising,\Nwe can’t seem to find them at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:17.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It means that they’re that crafty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:21.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Captains and Lieutenants\Nare keeping in close contact
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to obtain the latest\Nstatus report details.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:25.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! In that direction…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:28.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They found Jirobo\Nof the Squad 7 fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:29.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:35.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They’re gone…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:36.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:42.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Ichigo and the others are\Ndoing quite a number out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:44.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The security is getting tighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:51.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think we can handle\Nthose Soul Reapers now…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:53.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter, Uryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:58.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This Spirit Pressure…\NIt’s Ichigo, and the other one is…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:03.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji Abarai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:16.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo… You sure met up\Nwith a tough one…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:21.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.57,0:16:25.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel fine?\NAre you running a fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:28.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m okay, so don’t worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:29.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:34.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You space out sometimes,\Nso I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:36.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, that was no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:37.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:43.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good, then let’s hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:55.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo’s spiritual power is rising…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:01.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His opponent’s Spirit Pressure\Nis quite strong…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:03.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I had better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:29.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, you’re fighting\Nagainst a Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:33.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how strong you are,\Nyou can’t win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:33.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:39.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That may not be the case.\NPlease take a good look at Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:58.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible! He’s completely\Noverpowering Lieutenant Abarai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:03.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He… Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:06.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:09.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s what I’d like to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:12.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ichigo Kurosaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:16.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How do you plan on saving Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:18.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:23.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you defeat me here,\Nthere are still 11 Lieutenants left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:27.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And above them,\Nthere are 13 Captains.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:32.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you defeat them all,\Nthere’s no way to save Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:36.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And you think you can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:40.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Who cares\Nhow many Captains there are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:42.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or how many Lieutenants?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:44.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn’t matter! I’ll defeat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:48.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll defeat them all\Nif they get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:52.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that? Where do you\Nget your confidence from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:58.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so worked up over this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:00.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your Zanpaku-to has changed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:03.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t think you’re stronger\Njust because of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:06.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:07.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:16.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:18.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zabimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:32.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can’t stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:36.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:38.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:40.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:47.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to think…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:52.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that you already know my strength\Njust by fighting me once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:54.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:59.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When the ranked Lieutenants\Nand above are sent outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:03.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,our powers are severely limited
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:06.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so that we don’t adversely\Naffect the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:11.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My strength right now is\Nfive times greater than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:17.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So no matter how strong you become,\Nthere’s no way you can defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.71,0:20:29.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So that means that attack there…\Nwas the best you’ve got?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:45.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t affect me! Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:53.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! If 11 of these are\Nwhat I’m dealing with,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:56.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:04.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:41.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I looked up into the night sky\Nand saw a comet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.81,0:21:48.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you right now,\Nbut I can't fly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:56.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I could become a comet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.42,0:22:01.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would fly across the sky… I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:08.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would circle the skies and shine over you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:13.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With this instantaneous light\Nthat will definitely reach you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.76,0:22:21.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I could become a comet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.01,0:22:24.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'll always stay close to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.76,0:22:26.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now and forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.96,0:22:34.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As I’ve said before,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.46,0:22:37.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we Soul Reapers have our powers\Nseverely limited in the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:41.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My strength right now is five times greater\Nthan it was when I last fought you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.21,0:22:43.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve been training and I’ve become\Nten times stronger than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.93,0:22:45.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then I’m a hundred times\Nstronger than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.70,0:22:47.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m a thousand times\Nstronger than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:48.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I’m ten thousand\Ntimes stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.74,0:22:50.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then I’m a hundred thousand\Ntimes stronger than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.46,0:22:52.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m a million times stronger\Nin addition to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:54.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, too bad, I’m plus\Nten million times stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.29,0:22:55.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then I’m a hundred\Nmillion times stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.92,0:22:57.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m infinite times stronger!